[The livestock Sterne (34F) vaccine is freely available in all countries. It
has been used before, see the events of Las Vagas some 3-4 years ago
when it was sold as a field isolate to a gullible private researcher.
Unfortunately we will see it more often now in the hands of hoaxers.
We have found that it has an unfortunate capacity to float around and
contaminate laboratories, as we have identified it in a number of
archived collections from various institutes [even though labelled as a
field isolate, and is why we never ever use it. Laboratory hygiene is
absolutely vital if you must use this vaccine in research. - Mod.MHJ
